SDAbstractTableModel
public class SDAbstractTableModel.IconSetterMask
extends SDAbstractTableModel.ActionMask

Class provides support for setting action icons on data rows. The mask contains information on the target column for the icon. If the discriminator test is true, the target column gets the icon. Else, the target column gets the alternate icon. If the icons are not declared in the mask, default icons from the model are used.
